  <summary date="2005-01-24T17:23:43Z" status="Introduced in House">Adoption Information Act - Amends the Public Health Service Act to require family planning service projects or programs, as a condition of receiving certain grants or contracts, to assure the Secretary of Health and Human Services that they will provide to each person who inquires about their services a pamphlet containing a comprehensive list of adoption centers in their State.

Directs the Secretary to prepare, annually update, and distribute such pamphlets to such projects or programs.</summary>
